			section.media#media
				.container
					.media__inner
						h2.media__title.mobile-only How we partied last time
						.media__videos
							.media__videos-wrap
								button.media__play
								button.media__prev
								.media__list
									.media__item
										video(data-url="/152/videos/1580252400/porsche-contest-2020", poster="img/poster-1.jpg").video
									.media__item
										video(data-url="/152/videos/1580252400/porsche-contest-2020-2", poster="img/poster-2.jpg").video
								button.media__next
						h2.media__title.desktop-only How we partied last time

			section.faq#faq
				.container
					.faq__inner
						h2.faq__title Rules #[br]and Conditions
						.faq__content
							ul.faq__list
								li.faq__item
									p.faq__item-caption Who takes part in the contest?
									.faq__item-text
										p All the affiliates of the AdCombo affiliate network are the participants. 
								li.faq__item
									p.faq__item-caption What offers should I manage traffic to?
									.faq__item-text 
										p You should manage your traffic to all offers of AdCombo, CTR.ru, and Ecombo Junior for all GEOs.
										p NB: there are special rates for some  offers. For instance, redirect offers have a reduction rate of x0.25. Contact your AM for more information. 
								li.faq__item
									p.faq__item-caption How does it work? 
									.faq__item-text
										p A new section in the user interface will appear. You’ll be able to check the current quantity of #[strong porsche points] you gained and your actual position in the Top-ranking table #[i (Top-10, Top-20 , Top-30, Top-40, Top-50 or under Top-50)]. 
										p The more #[strong porsche points] you get, the higher your position is.
								li.faq__item
									p.faq__item-caption What are the “porsche points” and how can I get them? 
									.faq__item-text
										p Porsche points are the contest currency. You get #[strong 1 Porsche Point] per each #[strong 10 000 USD] earned and available for withdrawal in your affiliate account. There are special rates for the conversion of funds into Porsche Points for some types of offers: #[strong (funds earned) x (offer rate)].
										p #[strong Example]: an affiliate has run traffic in the period from #[strong Feb 1, 2020, to Sep 1, 2020], inclusive and earned #[strong 350 000 USD] available for withdrawal. Hence, he got #[strong 35 Porsche Points].
										p #[strong ATTENTION]: An affiliate cannot get any #[strong Porsche Points] for unapproved or rejected leads as well as for the held funds.
								
							ul.faq__list
								li.faq__item
									p.faq__item-caption What changes will the AdCombo Loyalty Program face?
									.faq__item-text
										p The sum gained with the Loyalty Program will be on hold and not be available for withdrawal, but it will be displayed on the affiliate's dashboard and in the chart. 
										p The maximum percentage of the affiliate's income from the AdCombo Loyalty Program cannot be higher than 4%. 
								li.faq__item
									p.faq__item-caption Who can participate in the prize drawing?
									.faq__item-text
										p The affiliates entered TOP-50 by the end of the contest are eligible to take part in the prize draw at the party. 
										P NB: #[u Only those who are present at the final party can have a right to be full participants in the prize drawing]. 
										p The date and time of the party will be announced later. Don't miss the updates!
										p #[strong ATTENTION]: AdCombo undertakes to provide the participants from the Top-50 with free accommodation at the venue of the final party at its expense. All travel expenses are paid by the participants themselves.
								li.faq__item
									p.faq__item-caption How many prizes can a prize draw participant win? 
									.faq__item-text
										p Each participant of the prize drawing is able to win 1 additional prize and 1 grand prize (one of the two Porsche sports cars). 
								li.faq__item
									p.faq__item-caption What is the procedure of choosing a winner?
									.faq__item-text
										p The winner is chosen by a draw.
										p Each of the prize draw participants receives chips with its nickname registered in the AdCombo network. #[strong A quantity of participant`s chips is equal to the number of gained Porsche Points.]
										p The chips of all the prize draw participants are put into a lottery drum. The drawing for the additional prizes is conducted first. Then the drawing of the grand prizes starts. #[strong The more chips are gained the higher the chances to win!]

						.faq__other
							p Follow our news and updates and send a ticket request to your personal manager or contact AdCombo Support if you have a question to ask. 
							p The AdCombo affiliate network reserves the right to impose restrictions toward incoming traffic or suspend it temporarily due to the technical need of the traffic processing system. Moreover, AdCombo is able to set caps on offers or place a limit on the number of leads.
							p For more information, please contact your personal affiliate manager.  

